					"uidString" : "fDwPsYYlR+62R2iY6AYqsQ=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "Glamorous Toolkit is an environment for humans to make sense of systems through tools built contextually to match specific situations. Controlling the environment through which we perceive our systems allows us to influence how we think about them. LLMs are a new kind of system, and working with them follows the same principles in a slightly different form. Moreover, the perfromance of LLMs themselves benefit from these principles, too."
			},
